# Windows Terminal Style Demo
# Windows terminal appearance

Output examples/dvds/windows-style.svg

Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 15
Set Title "PowerShell"
Set Template windows
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[32mPS>\x1b[0m "

Type "Get-ChildItem"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "Write-Host 'Hello from Windows!' -ForegroundColor Cyan"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
